      <title>纽约市将于数周内宣布新的校园手机禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/nyc-set-to-announce-new-school-ban-on-cellphones-within-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市正在考虑恢复禁止学生使用手机的禁令，因为全国范围内越来越多的人担心手机会分散学生的学习注意力并损害他们的心理健康。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/nyc-set-to-announce-new-school-ban-on-cellphones-within-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:24:29 GMT</pubDate>
