      <title>机器人、无人机和无人驾驶拖拉机开启农业新时代</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/farming-goes-high-tech-with-driverless-tractors-drones-robots-de-agco-cnh</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拖拉机在卫星和 iPhone 的引导下耕作农田，无需驾驶员。太阳能机器人像巨大的户外扫地机器人一样在地面上照料植物，而无人机则在上空飞行，为农作物喷洒农药。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/farming-goes-high-tech-with-driverless-tractors-drones-robots-de-agco-cnh</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
