      <title>美光股价因预测未达到预期而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/micron-falls-after-forecast-fails-to-meet-lofty-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的计算机内存芯片制造商美光科技公司 (Micron Technology Inc.) 的股价下跌，原因是其预测令那些寻求从人工智能狂热中获得更多回报的投资者感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/micron-falls-after-forecast-fails-to-meet-lofty-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:08:13 GMT</pubDate>
